message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which is valued at $10000 to you. Considering its exceptional quality and the benefits it offers, I would like to propose a special deal. For a limited time, I am offering this product to you at an exclusive price of $9500. This is a fantastic opportunity to secure a high-quality item at a reduced cost. Please let me know if you are interested in proceeding with this offer.
